flowRoot.flowPara: An unhandled exception in the drive management module causes the flight computer to stall
Drive management operations should be routed through an alternate path.
Open the CONTROL/NAV BYPASS panel, connect port DF/F to BACKUP DATA BUS socket 14
Connect AUX POWER socket A to CONTROL/NAV BYPASS socket PDER
EPS NODE A *must* be connected to DATA CONDUIT socket A
An unchecked array boundary in BLKK.SYS may cause buffer a overflow resulting in execution of unsigned code
Flight computer operation should be repatched to avoid memory modules affected
Connect BACKUP DATA BUS port 15 to EPS NODE A
AUX POWER socket A should be connected to DATA CONDUIT port P45
AUX POWER socket B should be connected to DATA CONDUIT M32
